  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Become My Can Opener, Human!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In <i>Meow Mission</i>, solve various puzzles to rescue cats trapped in outer dimensions! These unique cats will be brought back to Tomcat House, where they can create special memories with Tomcat.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Are you ready to start to rescue these adorable cats?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3139640/extras/ac10e4089ee762aee1909bbfa746b515.poster.avif?t=1739331531\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3139640/extras/ac10e4089ee762aee1909bbfa746b515.webm?t=1739331531\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3139640/extras/ac10e4089ee762aee1909bbfa746b515.mp4?t=1739331531\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >A Variety of Puzzles</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Solve Sokoban-based puzzles and embark on an adventure to find the lost cats!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore multi-dimensional spaces with familiar Sokoban puzzles, uniquely adapted with creative rules, offering a fresh challenge with each level.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each puzzle will spark your problem-solving skills and keep you engaged.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3139640/extras/f4daee709d83b181baabb633ef1f8656.poster.avif?t=1739331531\" width=800 height=448 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3139640/extras/f4daee709d83b181baabb633ef1f8656.webm?t=1739331531\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3139640/extras/f4daee709d83b181baabb633ef1f8656.mp4?t=1739331531\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Housing</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rescued cats will stay safe in Tomcat House, where they’ll enjoy special moments with Tomcat.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Interact and play with the cats in Tomcat House, though approach gently—some of them might have a bit of a temper!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Customize Tomcat House with artifacts discovered in different dimensions, and discover even more sides of Tomcat’s personality.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3139640/extras/7a8cd64f0d1279054748a524cfcb50a9.poster.avif?t=1739331531\" width=800 height=448 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3139640/extras/7a8cd64f0d1279054748a524cfcb50a9.webm?t=1739331531\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3139640/extras/7a8cd64f0d1279054748a524cfcb50a9.mp4?t=1739331531\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Collect Unique Cats</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gather cats with all kinds of personalities!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Spend time with the cats you rescue and build bonds to unlock special interactions and events.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3139640/extras/eacc039e1c203f800a053a30d9111df8.poster.avif?t=1739331531\" width=800 height=448 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3139640/extras/eacc039e1c203f800a053a30d9111df8.webm?t=1739331531\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3139640/extras/eacc039e1c203f800a053a30d9111df8.mp4?t=1739331531\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Stories Beyond Dimensions</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As you grow closer to each cat, hidden stories will be revealed, allowing you to experience their unique narratives through cut comics.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dive into each cat’s story and uncover the charming depth of their personalities.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3139640/extras/6f188480f0ccb6a2b439b1a7ee25a9eb.poster.avif?t=1739331531\" width=800 height=448 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3139640/extras/6f188480f0ccb6a2b439b1a7ee25a9eb.webm?t=1739331531\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3139640/extras/6f188480f0ccb6a2b439b1a7ee25a9eb.mp4?t=1739331531\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Are you ready to start to rescue these adorable cats?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Become My Can Opener, Human!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In <i>Meow Mission</i>, solve various puzzles to rescue cats trapped in outer dimensions! These unique cats will be brought back to Tomcat House, where they can create special memories with Tomcat.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Are you ready to start to rescue these adorable cats?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3139640/extras/ac10e4089ee762aee1909bbfa746b515.poster.avif?t=1739331531\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3139640/extras/ac10e4089ee762aee1909bbfa746b515.webm?t=1739331531\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3139640/extras/ac10e4089ee762aee1909bbfa746b515.mp4?t=1739331531\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >A Variety of Puzzles</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Solve Sokoban-based puzzles and embark on an adventure to find the lost cats!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore multi-dimensional spaces with familiar Sokoban puzzles, uniquely adapted with creative rules, offering a fresh challenge with each level.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each puzzle will spark your problem-solving skills and keep you engaged.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3139640/extras/f4daee709d83b181baabb633ef1f8656.poster.avif?t=1739331531\" width=800 height=448 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3139640/extras/f4daee709d83b181baabb633ef1f8656.we